{"id":"sirion","term":"Sirion","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A breastplate, the Sidonian name of Hermon (q.v.), <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Deuteronomy 3:9\">Deut. 3:9</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 29:6\">Ps. 29:6</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Deuteronomy 3:9","Psalms 29:6"]}